00:14:32,703 --> 00:14:35,546
Games that emphasize fine art processes

223
00:14:35,606 --> 00:14:38,429
in their asset creation have both creative novelty

224
00:14:38,930 --> 00:14:41,012
and can get your game displayed in museums

225
00:14:41,092 --> 00:14:42,354
and other institutions.

226
00:14:44,929 --> 00:14:48,631
Art-inspired games have and can, or can and have,

227
00:14:48,931 --> 00:14:50,731
provided meaningful collaborations,

228
00:14:51,112 --> 00:14:54,433
allowing art professionals a real seat at the table

229
00:14:54,733 --> 00:14:56,554
and mechanic designers to discover

230
00:14:56,634 --> 00:14:58,074
new methods of interactivity.

