00:15:09,485 --> 00:15:11,906
As for teaching, software is necessary,

235
00:15:11,986 --> 00:15:13,947
but we should blend the fine arts

236
00:15:13,987 --> 00:15:15,308
into the core of teaching it.

237
00:15:15,888 --> 00:15:17,989
Use software as a tool for practicing the arts

238
00:15:18,049 --> 00:15:19,750
and teach your students to do the same.

239
00:15:20,470 --> 00:15:22,131
We can do this by designing projects

