733
00:46:30,959 --> 00:46:36,582
I'm talking about a deeper, more fundamental reimagining of our roles and changing the

734
00:46:36,642 --> 00:46:38,343
structure that we create in our classrooms.

735
00:46:39,310 --> 00:46:40,712
the form of power that we exert.

736
00:46:41,593 --> 00:46:44,796
